oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Johnny Rodriguez at the Colonial Theater
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Metal photoplates; Rodriguez, Johnny, 1951-;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black and red on white) announcing Johnny Rodriguez and the Music City Band at the Country Music Jamboree at the Colonial Theatre on July 18 and 19. Poster features a metal photoplate of Johnny Rodriguez. Poster was printed for job no. 16633. For additional information about this poster see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/28198.
